Number of followers (i.e. Replicas) to which replication is currently paused to help them recover from I/O overload.Such Replicas will be ignored for the purposes of proposal quota, and will notreceive replication traffic. They are essentially treated as offline for thepurpose of replication. This serves as a crude form of admission control.The count is emitted by the leaseholder of each range.
